==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rutaceous
<hw>Ru*ta"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rutaceous</ets>, from <ets>ruta</ets> rue. See <er>Rue</er> the
plant.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to plants of a
natural order (<ord>Rutaceae</ord>) of which the rue is the type, and
which includes also the orange, lemon, dittany, and buchu.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

